<p class="slogan" id="slogan">
class attribute is most commonly used to point style in css
id attribute most commonly used in javascript
both can be used in css and javascript


<div>
	..other html elements
</div>
div element is normally used as a container for other elements
it can be used to structure and style part of a layout

Semantic elements
<form> <header>, <section>
<div> <span> are not semantic tags

